author: Carol E. Lee
title: Pakistani Prime Minister Meets With Obama
text:
WASHINGTON—President Barack Obama hosted Pakistani Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif at the White House on Thursday for a meeting the president described as an “opportunity to further deepen the relationship” between the two countries.
